prefuse.data.parser
类 IntArrayParser

java.lang.Object
  prefuse.data.parser.IntArrayParser
所有已实现的接口：
DataParser
public class IntArrayParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataParser

DataParser instance the parses an array of int values from a text string. Values are expected to be comma separated and can be within brackets, parentheses, or curly braces.

作者：
jeffrey heer
